            </a>Upgrade Testing - Post Flare 12</h3>
        <p>The below steps are used to test the Flare upgrade process post Flare 12.</p>
        <ol>
            <li>Close Flare. </li>
            <li>Go to any pre Flare 12 installation folder (e.g. C:\Program Files (x86)\MadCap Software\MadCap Flare V11\Flare.app\Version)</li>
            <li>Copy the Version.mcversion file to your desktop and open the file in Notepad.</li>
            <li>Enter 11, 22, 33, and 44 for Major , Minor, Build, and Revision respectively. (e.g. Major="11" Minor="22" Build="33" Revision="44")</li>
            <li>Save the file with the filename Flare.mcversion. </li>
            <li>Copy Flare.mcversion to the same location as Flare.exe for the upgrade test.</li>
            <li>Launch Flare. </li>
            <li>You will be prompted to install updates.</li>
